like acne or hyperpigmentation. For oily, acne-prone skin, we recommend the&nbsp;<span style="background-color: rgb(255, 226, 240);"><a href="https://koreanskincare.co.uk/products/iunik-tea-tree-relief-serum" class="" style="" data-position="6">&nbsp;IUNIK Tea Tree Relief Serum</a></span>, which contains 67% tea tree extract to soothe and heal blemishes. It's also infused with centella asiatica and niacinamide, which help to calm redness and brighten the skin.</p><p></p><p></p></div></div><div data-label="Heading" data-key="heading" data-atomgroup="element" id="e-1730300422520" class="element-wrap" data-icon="gpicon-heading" data-ver="2" data-id="1730300422520" style=""><lt-highlighter contenteditable="false" class="lt--mac-os" data-lt-linked="1" style="display: none; z-index: auto !important;"><lt-div spellcheck="false" class="lt-highlighter__wrapper" style="width: 847.5px !important; height: 28.0781px !important; transform: none !important; transform-origin: 423.75px 14.0391px !important; zoom: 1 !important;"><lt-div class="lt-highlighter__scroll-element" style="top: 0px !important; left: 0px !important; width: 847.5px !important; height: 31px !important;"></lt-div></lt-div></lt-highlighter><div class="elm text-edit gf-elm-center gf-elm-left-md gf-elm-left-sm gf-elm-left-xs gf-elm-left-lg" data-gemlang="en" data-exc="" data-lt-tmp-id="lt-398977" spellcheck="false" data-gramm="false"><h3 class="gf_gs-text-heading-3">Moisturise</h3></div></div><div data-label="Text Block" data-key="text-block" data-atomgroup="element" id="e-1730300422540" class="element-wrap" data-icon="gpicon-textblock" data-ver="1" data-id="1730300422540" style=""><lt-highlighter contenteditable="false" class="lt--mac-os" data-lt-linked="1" style="display: none; z-index: auto !important;"><lt-div spellcheck="false" class="lt-highlighter__wrapper" style="width: 847.5px !important; height: 768px !important; transform: none !important; transform-origin: 423.75px 384px !important; zoom: 1 !important;"